, 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 'Latanoprost, Apraclonidine, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Physostigmine, Acetylcholine, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Brinzolamide, Brimonidine, Levobunolol', 1767369485);
